metadata.name: "BRAIN STORM"
metadata.description:
There are many thoughts swirling in my head. I try not to let them out and it's getting harder and harder to do it hour by hour. Sometimes I think my head is going to explode from everything that's going on.
...
Unfortunately, I can't control everything that happens. People cannot stop a lightning strike or a thunderclap. We try to remain calm, but the hurricane inside us breaks out. The time will come and I will release his consciousness.
...
BRAIN STORM.
Collection "New Era" 3\10
NFT consists of 2 pictures 420 x 594 mm.
Drawn by hand. Used black ink, watercolors.
